{"tid":1100568,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#169：世界大戰抹黑宇宙了","createTime":"2019-04-10T13:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T13:16:30.000Z","uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f66d4911fbcd31b1dc3fc17228e525ac2dbdd39f","tid":1100568,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:11:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LIHK乃PO呼籲:<br />\n反蓮反月應當悔改<br />\n</span></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu178O9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu178O9.jpg&h=a1edcbdd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQCjDoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQCjDoP.jpg&h=3b0827e5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fAk2JsW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAk2JsW.jpg&h=77299014&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生,二期生,三期生以及四期生在內，團體目前共有48名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=6a0d2dca\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n乃木坂46 4thアルバム<br />\n「今が思い出になるまで」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4月17日發售</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kqhku9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqhku9p.jpg&h=5f547f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 高山一実 2nd写真集「独白」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rRpcUAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrRpcUAe.jpg&h=d4cac450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 生田絵梨花 2nd写真集「インターミッション」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tok5x5r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTok5x5r.png&h=50b70e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 北野日奈子ファースト写真集 「空気の色」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gPlzise.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgPlzise.jpg&h=379fa89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 井上小百合ファースト写真集 「存在」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cdBjIT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcdBjIT6.jpg&h=c461748b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 22ndシングル<br />\n「帰り道は遠回りしたくなる」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2GkiUls.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2GkiUls.jpg&h=a5ad3116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 22ND VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76HLJPT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76HLJPT.png&h=813f0145&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46 四期生</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjUnHMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNjUnHMj.jpg&h=61687ed4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=ac1a0fc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，但不要幻想他會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦?<br />\n請大家支持日向坂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<del><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=0ae269b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing</a></del><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ns1NdRm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNs1NdRm.png&h=61cb3eef&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"41e37f3d3cdfa2d97ee55ed9fc4ce8587e3edaf0","tid":1100568,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"誤中1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694c754031bda8b3dd0ed6a97e457829816df89a","tid":1100568,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:12:32.000Z","msg":"打丁打到唔記得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2cd22c5b53ede539cf23f87f641b3741560c52","tid":1100568,"uid":34304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"以為無人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998ce089804f5e22de7a2d4b3e2d6d491dd0c7b0","tid":1100568,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"一撳入去已經揮緊手講byebye<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw雙馬尾日奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohpLrtP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohpLrtP.png&h=5457b04c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00b61a50df0c4ce07de39d88a8d83bd8a3de1fa7","tid":1100568,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"reply